pullrequest.title: Remove override of OnVisibilityChange for display plugins

content.raw: Looks good to me. The homebrew build is failing though because we need a new ign-rendering bottle. [Here](https://github.com/osrf/homebrew-simulation/pull/450/files)'s an example of a PR bumping the bottle's commit. Let me know if you need help, I've only done this a few times myself.
